<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA522_11_su_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema522_11_su.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_11_su_0003">
        <section class="title type2">
            <h2 data-type="1" data-text="자기주도 3">
                <span class="blue line" lang="y">내 힘으로 풀어요</span>
                <span lang="y">공부한 내용을 확인해요</span>
            </h2>
        </section>

        <section class="title type2 jgjd_3_sub_title">
            <h2 data-head="1" lang="y" class="fraction-line-1">
                <div class="title_row">
                    <span class="mixed_fraction ml_0">
                        <span>3&times;1</span>
                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>5</span></span>
                    </span>
                    <span>를 두 가지 방법으로 계산하려고 합니다.</span>
                    <span class="nemo_blank"></span>
                    <span>안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</span>
                </div>
            </h2>
        </section>

        <section class="contents paging_layout">
            <div class="input_area">
                <article class="page page_1">
                    <div class="question_box align_start dir_col">
                        <div class="tit">
                            <span class="label"><i>방법1</i></span>
                            <span class="tit_txt">대분수를 자연수와 진분수의 합으로 나타내어 계산하기​</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mixed_fraction f32b m_auto gap_0">
                            <span>3&times;1</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span>2</span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </span>
                            =
                            <div class="pare_wrap">3&times;1</div>
                            +
                            <div class="pare_wrap">
                                3&times;
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>2</span>
                                    <span>5</span>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            =
                            <span class="input_wrap">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                            </span>
                            +
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span class="input_wrap">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                                </span>
                                <span>
                                    <span>5</span>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                            =
                            <span class="input_wrap">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                            </span>
                            +
                            <span class="input_wrap">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                            </span>
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span class="input_wrap">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                                </span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </span>
                            =
                            <span class="input_wrap">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
                            </span>
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span class="input_wrap">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                                </span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_2">
                    <div class="question_box align_start dir_col">
                        <div class="tit">
                            <span class="label"><i>방법2</i></span>
                            <span class="tit_txt">대분수를 가분수로 나타내어 계산하기​</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mixed_fraction f32b m_auto gap_0">
                            <span>3&times;1</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span>2</span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </span>
                            =
                            <div class="pare_wrap">
                                3
                            </div>
                            &times;
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span class="input_wrap">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                                </span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </span>
                            =
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span>
                                    <span class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                    </span>
                                    &times;
                                    <span class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </span>
                            =
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span class="input_wrap">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="21"></math-field>
                                </span>
                                <span>
                                    <span>5</span>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                            =
                            <span class="input_wrap">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
                            </span>
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span class="input_wrap">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                                </span>
                                <span>
                                    <span>5</span>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>

            <div class="btn_area">
                <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
                <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
                <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>